data.description: Move in ready, seller can close quickly, vacant. New paint, carpet, engineered hardwood floors, 1st floor primary bedroom.  Converted garage can be easily converted back to garage.  Open floor plan.  New stainless steel appliances. Surround sound through out the whole house.  New garbage disposal.  Water heater 1 year old.  All the bedrooms have walk in closets and much more. View of the pond. Fees includes water, sewer, trash pickup, ground maintenance, clubhouse with exercise room and pool.  Near all of the shops, interstate and eateries to enjoy.  Make this your home today!
